                </li>
              </ul>
            </li>
            <li>
              <em>Birds That Hunt and Are Hunted</em> (1898).
              <ul>
                <li>
                  <a
                    href="https://archive.org/details/birdsthathuntare00bla"
                    target="_blank"
                    rel="noopener noreferrer">Internet Archive (1st edition)</a>
                </li>
                <li>
                  <a
                    href="https://archive.org/details/birdsthathuntar00blan"
                    target="_blank"
                    rel="noopener noreferrer">Internet Archive (alt)</a>
                </li>
                <li>
                  <a
                    href="https://archive.org/details/birdsthathuntare00doubrich"
                    target="_blank"
                    rel="noopener noreferrer">Internet Archive (Doubleday
                    scan)</a>
                </li>
                <li>
                  <a
                    href="https://catalog.hathitrust.org/Record/001501431"
                    target="_blank"
                    rel="noopener noreferrer">HathiTrust</a>
                </li>
              </ul>
            </li>
            <li>
              <em>How to Attract the Birds</em> (1902).
              <ul>
                <li>
                  <a
                    href="https://archive.org/details/howtoattractbird00bla"
                    target="_blank"
                    rel="noopener noreferrer">Internet Archive</a>
                </li>
              </ul>
            </li>
            <li>
              <em>Birds Every Child Should Know</em>.
              <ul>
                <li>
